Random Die
    New random (1-6) +1

Board
    -10 to 10.
        1-10 = player side
        -9 to 10 = enemy side

Player moves the amount

Player options
    Forward
    Retreat
        if player on own side, gain 250 ammo per die roll
        hasBomb = false (on own side) gain a new one.

    Attack (100 times, the number on die)
        If player 0 fields away from enemy, kill 6 troops
        If player 1 field away from enemy, kill 5 troops etc.